<p>Kourtney Kardashian is the eldest of the three Kardashian sisters.  She is a mother and takes a primary role in the management of DASH Boutiques.  Her personal style is easy to relate to - compared to younger sisters Kloe and Kim Kardashian.  Kourtney Kardashian dates a regular guy and is seemingly more down to earth.  Kourtney Kardashian is a major focus on all episodes of the popular reality-TV series "Keeping Up With The Kardashians" and subsequent spinoffs.  She appears on many major meida outlets and talk shows promoting the various Kardashian family business ventures and products.</p>
