<p>In addition to being a founder and main spokesperson of DASH Boutiques, Kim Kardashian has a very busy career.  With numerous endorsemnt deals with several national brands, Kim seems to be the most brand popular of all the three Kardashian sisters.  If you see DASH Kim Kardashian clothing online, other than K-DASH on QVC or Kardashian Kollection through Sears, it is probably NOT authentic.  There are a few clothing products by BeBe as well.  DASH Kim Kardashian counterfeit goods are on the rise, so be weary when shopping online.</p>
<h1>Kim Kardashian Modeling</h1>
<p>Since her nude appearance in a 2007 edition of <em>Playboy</em> magazine, Kim Kardashian has landed several modeling gigs in the fashion world.  These experiences have led to larger scale business, retail, and film ventures.<p>
<h3>Some Of These Include:</h3>
