<h1>Kim Kardashian Personal Life</h1>
<p>Kim Kardashian was married in the year 2000 to music producer Damon Thomas.  This marriage lasted four years and ended in divorce in 2004.  Kim Kardashian has had relationships since with other personalities in the media.  Shortly after her divorce there was Ray J, brother of singer Brandy.  More recently short lived marriage to NBA Basketball player Kris Humphries.  This marriage ended in divorce as well - less than three months after their much publicized wedding in 2011.</p>
