<small><em>Image courtesy of celebuzz.com</em></small>
<h1>Khloe Kardashian Marriage</h1>
<p>Khloe Kardashian and Lamar Odom from the NBA, were married on September 27, 2009.  Following the event, maid of honor and sister Kim Kardashian Tweeted "Khloe & Lamar's wedding was a night to remember!".  Despite only a short 3-month courtship - two years later, the couple remains intact. On her wedding day, Khloe Kardashian was dressed in a Vera Wang dress.</p>
