";s:10:"post_title";s:6:"K DASH";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:6:"k-dash";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2012-07-13 05:57:54";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2012-07-13 12:57:54";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:48:"http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/?page_id=425";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:13;O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:345;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2011-12-18 15:38:19";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2011-12-18 23:38:19";s:12:"post_content";s:2131:"<p>DASH and Kardashian are two distinct brands.  It is commonly confused the two - DASH and Kardashian.  Initially there was D-A-S-H.  That is the brand known as DASH. True DASH womens clothing and accessories are not available online currently.  DASH items as seen on the popular TV series and it's spinoffs are only available at the actual stores.  Have a clear understanding of the differences between DASH and Kardashian brand products when shopping online.</p>
<h1>DASH And Kardashian Clothing</h1>
<p>With the popularity of DASH and Kardashian exposure to big business channels, opportunities arose in the fashion/apparel industry.  The Kardashians do brand out their name to certain outlets.  This is where DASH and Kardashian branded apparel begin to differ.  Kardashian Kollection is an authorized brand by the Kardashians that is available through Sears.  The stock a full line of Kardashian branded products including womens apparel, accessories, and bath & body items.  The price ranges are more accessible than that of DASH and Kardashian approved to boot.  The Kardashian Kollection has over 200 different items in it all bearing and promoted by the Kardashian sisters.</p>
<h1>DASH And Kardashian K-DASH</h1>
<p>K-DASH is slightly confusing here.  K-DASH is not DASH, but is a closer resemblance to what is available at the boutiques than is the Kardashian Kollection.  DASH and Kardashian brands differ here in that the price is still mid range when it comes to K-DASH.  DASH is way more high end at the retail outlets.  Similar to Arcade Boutique, but not as big of a selection.  K-DASH is available as an exclusive through QVC.  Kim Kardashian and Kourtney are often seen on TV promoting these DASH and Kardashian branded spinoffs.</p>
<h1>Shopping Online For DASH And Kardashian</h1> 
<p>It is important to know when shopping online for DASH And Kardashian branded items, that there are a lot of vendors attempting to sell D-A-S-H / DASH and Kardashian brands that are fake.  Remember that DASH as seen on TV is not available online.  K-DASH and Kardashian Kollections are exclusive with QVC and Sears.</p>";s:10:"post_title";s:19:"DASH And Kardashian";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"dash-and-kardashian";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2012-07-20 19:15:41";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2012-07-21 02:15:41";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:14;s:4:"guid";s:48:"http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/?page_id=345";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:2:"16";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:14;O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:972;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2012-09-18 17:13:06";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2012-09-19 00:13:06";s:12:"post_content";s:17633:"<p>Kourtney Kardashian Clothes are hard to miss.  Her style selection in fashion varies from elegant to mommy cute.  Singer 22 brings all of these top of the line fashions to you online!  These are just some of the exclusive offerings found online that were seen on Kourtney Kardashian.</p>
