&nbsp;";s:10:"post_title";s:27:"Keep Up With The Kardashian";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:27:"keep-up-with-the-kardashian";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2012-07-19 21:31:12";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2012-07-20 04:31:12";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:47:"http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/?page_id=14";s:10:"menu_order";i:6;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"7";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}}s:32:"56d839b4685645734b8baa2ddfcae1be";a:28:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:345;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2011-12-18 15:38:19";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2011-12-18 23:38:19";s:12:"post_content";s:2131:"<p>DASH and Kardashian are two distinct brands.  It is commonly confused the two - DASH and Kardashian.  Initially there was D-A-S-H.  That is the brand known as DASH. True DASH womens clothing and accessories are not available online currently.  DASH items as seen on the popular TV series and it's spinoffs are only available at the actual stores.  Have a clear understanding of the differences between DASH and Kardashian brand products when shopping online.</p>
<h1>DASH And Kardashian Clothing</h1>
<p>With the popularity of DASH and Kardashian exposure to big business channels, opportunities arose in the fashion/apparel industry.  The Kardashians do brand out their name to certain outlets.  This is where DASH and Kardashian branded apparel begin to differ.  Kardashian Kollection is an authorized brand by the Kardashians that is available through Sears.  The stock a full line of Kardashian branded products including womens apparel, accessories, and bath & body items.  The price ranges are more accessible than that of DASH and Kardashian approved to boot.  The Kardashian Kollection has over 200 different items in it all bearing and promoted by the Kardashian sisters.</p>
<h1>DASH And Kardashian K-DASH</h1>
<p>K-DASH is slightly confusing here.  K-DASH is not DASH, but is a closer resemblance to what is available at the boutiques than is the Kardashian Kollection.  DASH and Kardashian brands differ here in that the price is still mid range when it comes to K-DASH.  DASH is way more high end at the retail outlets.  Similar to Arcade Boutique, but not as big of a selection.  K-DASH is available as an exclusive through QVC.  Kim Kardashian and Kourtney are often seen on TV promoting these DASH and Kardashian branded spinoffs.</p>
<h1>Shopping Online For DASH And Kardashian</h1> 
<p>It is important to know when shopping online for DASH And Kardashian branded items, that there are a lot of vendors attempting to sell D-A-S-H / DASH and Kardashian brands that are fake.  Remember that DASH as seen on TV is not available online.  K-DASH and Kardashian Kollections are exclusive with QVC and Sears.</p>";s:10:"post_title";s:19:"DASH And Kardashian";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"dash-and-kardashian";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2012-07-20 19:15:41";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2012-07-21 02:15:41";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:14;s:4:"guid";s:48:"http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/?page_id=345";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:2:"16";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:340;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2011-12-18 13:31:00";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2011-12-18 21:31:00";s:12:"post_content";s:2201:"<p>DASH by Kardashian is known the world over.  If you have experience with these boutiques, or have a general opinion to inform others about DASH By Kardashian share your thoughts below.  No one can deny that DASH by Kardashian has become a very successful brand in the area of women's fashion apparel and accessories.  The DASH by Kardashian Boutiques are major attractions in the three cities that they have opened.  Everything that happens in the brand receives national exposure with the show and then subsequent media coverage of the show.  This makes DASH by Kardashian a major industrial name.  DASH by Kardashian was initiated in 2006 and in that short time it has become one of the most sought after designer boutiques in the world.  What do you think about this?  Have you ever visited a DASH by Kardashian boutique?  We are curious to know.</p>
[caption id="attachment_314" align="aligncenter" width="493" caption="DASH by Kardashian"]<a href="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/dash-store.jpg"><img src="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/dash-store.jpg" alt="dash-by-kardashian" title="DASH by Kardashian" width="493" height="183" class="size-full wp-image-314" /></a>[/caption]

<h1>DASH By Kardashian - What is it?</h1>
<p>There are many opinions on why the DASH brand is popular.  The show obviously helps with sales at the boutiques, but people seem to support the Kardashian sisters characters and the business as a result of that loyalty.  What exactly is it?  We are curious to know what draws you to DASH by Kardashian.</p>
<h1>Rate DASH By Kardashian</h1>
<p>On the top of the comment form below you can rate the brand DASH by Kardashian.  Feel free to leave your thoughts as to why you like or dislike the brand.  In a short three year time period, DASH by Kardashian has take the fashion industry by storm.  It really is an industrial phenomena in terms of activity within a small brand.  Most importantly, if you have personally had some type of experience with the brand DASH by Kardashian, please do leave a rating.  Ratings help people to know where and where not to shop & spend their hard earned money.</p>  ";s:10:"post_title";s:18:"DASH By Kardashian";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:18:"dash-by-kardashian";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2012-09-26 13:41:03";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2012-09-26 20:41:03";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:86;s:4:"guid";s:48:"http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/?page_id=340";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"3";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:5;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2011-12-10 09:32:45";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2011-12-10 09:32:45";s:12:"post_content";s:2071:"<p>The DASH Clothing Boutique began in 2006 D-A-S-H in Calabasas, California.  This Original DASH in LA was very popular and considered not-mainstream and sheik. Due to the exploding popularity of the hit reality-TV series "<a href="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/keep-up-with-the-kardashian/">Keeping Up With The Kardashians</a>" things soon began to change.  Business increased and additional Boutiques were opened.  DASH Miami was opened in 2009 and more recently DASH New York opened for business in 2010.  All three stores have been very popular, meaning great success in retail.</p>
