<h1>DASH New York - Paparazzi Stop</h1>
<p>DASH NYC was the Kardashians third D-A-S-H Boutique and has become quite popular.  The location is in the heart of Soho and is classic modern decor and sheik.  Unlike the other D-A-S-H boutiques, this store gets celebrity visits and paparazzi more so than the other two DASH boutiques in Miami and LA. Waves of tourists or paparazzi happen from time to time, especially since in New York celebrities have easier access to the centrally located DASH NY in Manhattan.  The product line at DASH New York is more upscale including items such as tuxedos.</p>";s:10:"post_title";s:28:"DASH NYC - Ratings & Reviews";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:8:"dash-nyc";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2012-11-03 14:05:34";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2012-11-03 21:05:34";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:86;s:4:"guid";s:48:"http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/?page_id=180";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"4";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:9;O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:7;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2011-12-10 09:32:46";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2011-12-10 09:32:46";s:12:"post_content";s:3357:"<p>When searching for DASH Online, beware.  Beware at least until they relaunch a DASH Online shop.  For the most-part, DASH clothing that is on the shelves in the 3 physical locations is not available online.  The DASH Online Store never really got off the ground. It finally came to a total hault, when in the fall of 2009 <a href="http://ShopDashOnline.com" target="blank">ShopDASHOnline.com</a> was taken down.  There was no immediate or subsequent explanation for this.</p>
<h1>Searching For DASH Online ?</h1>
<p>When shopping online, be wary of potential counterfeiters.  There are only a few authorized distributors of Kardashian brand clothing.Â  <a href="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/k-dash/>K-DASH</a> by The Kardashians is offered by QVC as many of you have probably seen on television.  Beyond that several items from the Kardashian Kollection are available at Sears as of 2011.  Accessories such as Fragrences, Lotions, and Bathroom Accessories are more widespread with companies such as Kohls bearing items with the Kardashian name.</p>
