In spite of the movement to boycott "<a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/11/16/boycott-keeping-up-with-the-kardashians-online-petition-reality-show-off-air_n_1097165.html" target="blank"><em>Keeping Up With The Kardashians</em></a>" with 100,000+ signatures - To keep up with the Kardashian sisters can be tough. Kim &amp; Kourtney and Kloe are well received in New York. Following Kim's divorce to basketball guy Kris Whatever-His-Name-Is, several celebrities have shown public support for Kim. Rumors ran amuck that Kris publicly belittled Kim. Rumors are rumors, who knows? At any rate, it was good for ratings and apparently not a publicity stunt as some have reported. They truly grew to dislike each other, lol.

