Overall <em>Keeping Up With The Kardashians </em>reality show is a bit far from reality - for most.Â  DASH clothing line is however, very real.Â  The dream of freedom andÂ  family is still alive in the minds of many of the shows viewers.Â  Some may criticize the antics or excursiveness, but they are a tight knit family doing a lot of things that people aspire to do.Â  Hopefully if nothing else, it keeps the dream alive for many.Â  Even the haters will admit to a warm-fuzzy in the midst of a happy-family-funÂ  scene.Â  So Keep Up With The Kardashian crew this year and beyond.Â  <a title="New DASH Store - Melrose In LA" href="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/2012/07/new-dash-store-in-la-melrose/">DASH Melrose in LA</a> is now open.Â  Check it out!

