[caption id="attachment_200" align="alignleft" width="300"]<a href="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Khloe-Kardashian.jpg"><img src="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Khloe-Kardashian-300x294.jpg" alt="kloe-kardashian-dash" title="&lt;&lt;Khloe Kardashian&gt;&gt; on February 8, 2011 in Santa Monica, California." width="300" height="294" class="size-medium wp-image-200" /></a> Khloe At Her Book Signing In 2011[/caption]

<p>Khloe Kardashian has been on many major media outlets and continues to be a central character in the Kardashian Klan and hit reality-TV series "<em><a href="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/keep-up-with-the-kardashian/">Keeping Up With The Kardashians</a></em>", as well as spinoffs such as "Kourtney and Khloe take Miami".</p>
<h1>Khloe Kardashian and PETA</h1>
<p>In 2010 Khloe Kardashian was selected as a public figure by the organization PETA to protest animal abuses in the fashion industry.  Khloe seemed to be a perfect fit for this agenda, as she is a heavily exposed person, is in the fashion industry with DASH, and shares the feelings that animals should not be meant to suffer unnecessarily for the sake of luxury. In perhaps her most risque public appearance she appeared nude, but covered for a PETA photo shoot and public awareness campaign.  Khloe Kardashian is also known for her role as Spokeswoman for <em><a href="http://gan.doubleclick.net/gan_click?lid=41000000001360343&pid=SPM1627207101&adurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sears.com%2Fshc%2Fs%2Fp_10153_12605_SPM1627207101P&usg=AFHzDLv3aMsbFDEwatROE70A-tEcMiyLlA&pubid=21000000000354800">Quick Trim</a></em> dietary supplement.</p>
<h1>Khloe Kardashian Book</h1>
<p>Recently (December 2011) Khloe Kardashian appeared close by DASH LA at the Calabasas Barnes & Noble for a family booksigning of the most recent Kardashian release entitled "<em>Kardashian Konfidential</em>".  Sister Kourtney of DASH was along for the photo shoot.  Also in attendance were the younger sisters Kendall and Kylie.</p>
<img src="http://cdn4.khloekcdn.celebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Khloe-Kourtney-Kardashian-Calabasas-Book-Signing-0.jpg" alt="Khloe-kardashian-konfidential" /><br />
<small><em>Image courtesy of celebuzz.com</em></small>
<h1>Khloe Kardashian Marriage</h1>
<p>Khloe Kardashian and Lamar Odom from the NBA, were married on September 27, 2009.  Following the event, maid of honor and sister Kim Kardashian Tweeted "Khloe & Lamar's wedding was a night to remember!".  Despite only a short 3-month courtship - two years later, the couple remains intact. On her wedding day, Khloe Kardashian was dressed in a Vera Wang dress.</p>
[caption id="attachment_861" align="alignleft" width="200"]<a href="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/kloelamar.jpg"><img src="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/kloelamar.jpg" alt="Khloe-kardashian-lamar-odom" title="Khloe&amp; Lamar" width="200" height="311" class="size-full wp-image-861" /></a> Khloe Kardashian, owner of DASH boutique stores with husband Lamar Odom.  [/caption]
